00:00011144 D080            	   892: 	ADD.L	D0,D0
00:00011146 650001CC        	   893: 	BCS	QHOW		say "How?" if index is too big
00:0001114A D080            	   894: 	ADD.L	D0,D0
00:0001114C 650001C6        	   895: 	BCS	QHOW
00:00011150 2F00            	   896: 	MOVE.L	D0,-(SP)	save the index
